ENTREZ_GENE_ID: NCBI Entrez Gene database id of intended siRNA target gene
NCBI_GENE_SYMBOL: Official symbol of target NCBI Gene Id
CONTROL_AVERAGE_CTG_NORMALISED_TO_NT1_RO: Control (siRNA alone) CTG data for each replicate normalised to NT1, then averaged the normalised values across the 2 replicates. Average normalised control CTG values used to calculate robust Z-score.
CONTROL_Z_SCORE_BIN: Control robust Z-score binning classification: LC (low cell count): value (2) -2, Hi (high cell count): value (3) 2, and NC (no change): 2 (3) value (3) -2
DOX_AVERAGE_CTG_NORMALISED_TO_NT1_ROBUST: Doxorubicin treated (siRNA + Doxorubicin) CTG data for each replicate normalised to NT1, then averaged the normalised values across the 2 replicates. Average normalised control CTG values used to calculate robust Z-score.
DOX_Z_SCORE_BIN: Doxorubicin robust Z-score binning classification: LC (low cell count): value (2) -2, Hi (high cell count): value (3) 2, and NC (no change): 2 (3) value (3) -2
CONTROL_AVERAGE_CTG_NORMALISED_TO_NT1: Control (siRNA alone) CTG data for each replicate normalised to NT1, then averaged the normalised values across the 2 replicates.
CONTROL_AVERAGE_CTG_NORMALISED_TO_MOCK: Control (siRNA alone) CTG data for each replicate normalised to mock, then averaged the normalised values across the 2 replicates.
DOX_AVERAGE_CTG_NORMALISED_TO_NT1: Doxorubicin treated (siRNA + Doxorubicin) CTG data for each replicate normalised to NT1, then averaged the normalised values across the 2 replicates.
DOX_AVERAGE_CTG_NORMALISED_TO_MOCK: Doxorubicin treated (siRNA + Doxorubicin) CTG data for each replicate normalised to mock, then averaged the normalised values across the 2 replicates.
FOLD_CHANGE_RATIO_Z_SCORE: Robust Z-score calculated on the FOLD_CHANGE_RATIO
SEED_CLUSTER_MIRNA_SHARING_SEED: Seed cluster analysis (using Dharmacon's seed clusterer tool) results. Enrichment score cut-off (3) 8.
